<h6 id="a-elliptical-arc" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#a-elliptical-arc" aria-hidden="true">#</a> A（Elliptical Arc）</h6>
<p><code v-pre>A</code>命令用于画<code v-pre>弧形</code>，它可以截取<code v-pre>圆</code>或<code v-pre>椭圆</code>的<code v-pre>弧形</code>成的曲线</p>
<p><strong>语法：</strong> A rx ry x-axis-rotation large-arc-flag sweep-flag x y 或者 a rx ry x-axis-rotation large-arc-flag sweep-flag x y</p>
<p><strong>参数：</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>rx、ry 分别为<code v-pre>X</code>轴的半径和<code v-pre>Y</code>轴的半径</li>
<li>x-axis-rotation 为弧度在<code v-pre>X</code>轴的<code v-pre>旋转角度</code></li>
<li>large-arc-flag 决定弧线是<code v-pre>大于</code>还是<code v-pre>小于</code>180度，<code v-pre>0</code>表示<code v-pre>小角度弧</code>，<code v-pre>1</code>表示<code v-pre>大角度弧</code></li>
<li>sweep-flag 为<code v-pre>弧</code>的<code v-pre>方向</code>，<code v-pre>0</code>表示从起点到终点沿<code v-pre>逆时针</code>画弧，1表示从起点到终点沿<code v-pre>顺时针</code>画弧</li>
<li>x、y 为弧形的<code v-pre>终点</code></li>
</ul>

