<p><strong>语法：</strong> <code v-pre>&lt;radialGradient cx=&quot;&quot; cy=&quot;&quot; r=&quot;&quot; fx=&quot;&quot; fy=&quot;&quot;&gt;</code></p>
<p><strong>参数：</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><code v-pre>cx</code>、<code v-pre>cy</code>、<code v-pre>r</code>分别为圆的<code v-pre>坐标</code>和<code v-pre>半径</code>，也就是渐变的<code v-pre>范围</code></li>
